The massive stone pyramid before you is unlike anything you've ever seen before, save for it's eerie resemblance to an oversized Sith Holocron... It is encrested with ancient runes, and all four sides of the prism has a large flawless gemstone set near the vertex. The tip itself is made of an opaque crystal that glows with an inner light. Along the surface of each side lies a strange, mirky substance, similar to that of a makeshift portal of ancient origin, but making contact only yields a violent response, rendering ones appendage nigh devoured by whatever abyssal powers lay within..
